NOTICE OF MODIFICATIONS

This work contains modifications to the original IdentityServer4 project:

1. Multi-targeting for .NET 8.0 and .NET 10.0 (December 2024)
   - Updated project files for multi-framework support
   - Updated dependencies for .NET 10 compatibility
   - Migrated test infrastructure to Microsoft.Testing.Platform

2. Security Fixes (December 2024)
   - CVE-2024-39694: Fixed IsLocalUrl control character validation
     Adapted from IdentityServer8 by HigginsSoft (Alexander Higgins)

   - Username Enumeration Prevention: Sanitized login logs
     Adapted from IdentityServer8 by HigginsSoft (Alexander Higgins)

   - Backchannel Logout Token Fix: Corrected JSON structure
     Adapted from IdentityServer8 PR #57 by HigginsSoft (Alexander Higgins)

   - Extension Method Naming: Renamed IsNullOrEmpty to CollectionIsNullOrEmpty
     Adapted from IdentityServer8 PR #60 by HigginsSoft (Alexander Higgins)

   - Input Sanitization Framework: Added comprehensive sanitization
     Adapted from IdentityServer8 by HigginsSoft (Alexander Higgins)

3. JSON Serialization Migration (December 2024)
   - Migrated from Newtonsoft.Json to System.Text.Json
   - Updated all serializers, converters, and test code

4. Initial .NET 8.0 Migration (May 2024)
   - Updated all projects to .NET 8.0
   - Updated package references
   - Added "dn." prefix to package ID

